    de.intarsys.nativec.type.INativeObject

    public class NativePcscDword
extends de.intarsys.nativec.type.NativeNumber
    For some reason the DWord in PC/SC Lite header files is declared as 8 byte in 64 bit Linux. On all other platforms in this universe a DWord is 4 byte.
